TextEng: Your attackers, who were they?
Are there not enough guards to keep you safe?
Text: 널 안전하게 지킬 경비가 부족한 거야?

TextEng: Who says I rescued you? Hand over your gold...
Text: 내가 널 구했다고 누가 그래? 금화 내놔...

TextEng: What do you know about the prison?
You'd better go. Keep to the shadows.
Text: 가는 게 좋겠어. 그림자에 숨어서 가.

TextEng: Dose brutes - who dey be?
Da guards - dey no protect you?
What you know 'bout dat prison?
Ha! Me no rescue you - Me jus' better mugger!
Text: 하! 나 너 구한 거 아냐-나 그냥 더 실력 좋은 강도야!

TextEng: You go now. Stay quiet, yuh?
The Head Gaoler, is it?
Da Head Gaoler, huh?
Tunnels? What tunnels?
Huh? Tunnels?
Where's this estate?
Where dis 'state?
Who are you? What are you doing on the streets?
Text: 너 누구야? 거리에서 뭐 하는 거야?

TextEng: Who you be? What you doing out?
Do you need an escort to the District gates?
Me escort you to Dis'trick gates, yuh?
Text: 나 너 구역 문까지 데려다줄까, 응?

TextEng: Ssh, follow me.
Just stay here for a moment.
Uh, you come wit' me.
You stay here, yuh?
